text: Harouna Abou Demba Sy (born 31 December 1991) is a professional footballer who plays for Grenoble Foot 38 as a right back. Born in France, he represents Mauritania at international level. ==Career== Born in Mont-Saint-Aignan, France, Sy has played for Sedan B, Reims B, Boulogne B, Boulogne, Amiens B and GS Consolat.
